title: Ep. 56 - Why Stocks Will Move Higher in 2011
itunes:title: Why Stocks Will Move Higher in 2011
description: Alex Green, Chief Investment Strategist at Oxford Club, talks about the Euro/Dollar relationship and why stocks will move higher in 2011. Braden Copeland, co-manager of the Stansberry Investment Advisory, tells us his favorite picks for next year.
